# ContextKit (MVP)

Content-addressed, reproducible **Context Packs** for reusing LLM analysis sessions.

## Quick start

```bash
# (recommended) using uv
uv venv && source .venv/bin/activate
uv pip install -e .

# or pip
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
```

```bash
# Initialize folders (optional; created lazily)
mkdir -p packs chats artifacts/sql artifacts/code artifacts/text resources/schema resources/data_manifests index .contextkit

# Fingerprint schema (example: Postgres)
ctx schema fingerprint --from postgres://user:pass@host:5432/dbname

# Save a chat
ctx save-chat --project demo --title "Returns vs LTV" --from samples/example_chat.md --schema postgres://user:pass@host:5432/dbname

# Summarize to a ContextPack
ctx summarize chats/2025-09-07--returns-vs-ltv.md

# Find & inject
ctx find "ltv returns cohort" --project demo
ctx inject packs/returns-vs-ltv--<hash>.md --validate-schema postgres://user:pass@host:5432/dbname
```

Set `OPENAI_API_KEY` in `.env` to enable LLM summarization; otherwise a heuristic summarizer is used.
